    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking for a new home for my awesome car! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape, ready for many more miles of adventures. It drives beautifully and has been well-cared for. If you\u2019re looking for a great deal on a dependable vehicle that still looks and feels wonderful, this is the one for you! Come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
