    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S features the desirable 3.4L flat-six M97 engine, delivering a linear power band through a 6-speed manual transaxle. The mid-engine architecture provides an ideal polar moment of inertia, complemented by a factory-spec McPherson strut suspension that retains its damping integrity. This example boasts crisp throttle response via VarioCam Plus variable valve timing and robust deceleration from four-piston monobloc calipers. Recent preventative maintenance includes a transaxle fluid flush and inspection of the AOS system. A mechanically sound driver\u2019s car that offers communicative steering feedback and exceptional chassis balance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for immediate sale.",
