      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust driver\u2019s car powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides tactile shifts, sending power through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. While the exterior displays minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with an honest 'good' condition rating, the drivetrain remains exceptionally tight. It features a refreshed suspension setup for neutral handling and precise turn-in, making it an ideal candidate for the purist seeking analog performance without the premium of a garage queen.",
